# ---- Rust / Cargo ----
# Compiled files and executables
debug/
target/

# Backup files generated by rustfmt
**/*.rs.bk

# MSVC Windows builds of rustc generate these, which store debugging information
*.pdb

# Generated by cargo mutants
**/mutants.out*/

# Cargo lockfile is kept for binaries (default); uncomment to ignore for libraries
# Cargo.lock

# ---- Editors / IDEs ----
# RustRover / IntelliJ
.idea/
*.iml

# VS Code
.vscode/
*.code-workspace

# Vim / Emacs
*.swp
*.swo
*~
\#*\#
.\#*

# Sublime
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace

# ---- OS files ----
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# ---- Environment / Secrets ----
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key

# ---- Logs / Coverage / Misc ----
*.log
logs/
coverage/
*.profraw
*.profdata

# ---- Documentation build output (cargo doc) ----
# Allow committing /docs source, but ignore generated output
/doc/
